_sText:
This was my entry for the www.interlopers.net fy map pack.

We wanted to put some of our talent together to prove that FY maps don't always have to be a pile of crap.

Unfortunatly i'm not a mapper. Whilst i do moderate the boards over there i'm a modeller and as such found making this map a bit of a pain. Also it didn't come out that well.

It was rushed towards the end (mainly because i spent most of my time making the textures) but it's playable

I highly recomend playing this map with a limited amount of players as it's not really suited for large games.

All weapons are available except for the AWP.

Other maps from the fy map pack can be found:
